dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: The Schools data set shows public and private schools in Snohomish County. The list was compiled from a variety of sources, including Washington State, school-oriented web sites, and the yellow pages.  Point locations are registered to the Integrated Land Records parcels and 2002/2003 digital orthophotos. Attributes include school name, address, administrative contact, and other information.
